    <item>
      <title>Docs: Imagecontentmode</title>
      <link>https://zupit.github.io/docs-beagle/docs/api/components/ui/image/imagecontentmode/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://zupit.github.io/docs-beagle/docs/api/components/ui/image/imagecontentmode/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It&amp;rsquo;s an &lt;code&gt;ENUM&lt;/code&gt; class responsible to define how the stated image will be visualized on UI.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&#34;nav nav-tabs&#34; id=&#34;t127&#34; role=&#34;tablist&#34;&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;nav-item&#34;&gt;&lt;a data-toggle=&#34;tab&#34; class=&#34;nav-link active&#34; href=&#34;#t127-0&#34; role=&#34;tab&#34; aria-controls=&#34;t127-0&#34; aria-selected=&#34;true&#34;&gt;Kotlin DSL&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	  &lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;tab-content&#34; id=&#34;t127&#34;&gt;&lt;div id=&#34;t127-0&#34; class=&#34;tab-pane show active&#34; role=&#34;tabpanel&#34; aria-labelledby=&#34;t127-0&#34;&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre style=&#34;background-color:#f8f8f8;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-kotlin&#34; data-lang=&#34;kotlin&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#204a87;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;enum&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#204a87;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#000&#34;&gt;ImageContentMode&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#000;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#000&#34;&gt;FIT_XY&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#000;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#000&#34;&gt;FIT_CENTER&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#000;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#000&#34;&gt;CENTER_CROP&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#000;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#000&#34;&gt;CENTER&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span style=&#34;color:#000;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It can be configured as &lt;code&gt;FIT_XY&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;FIT_CENTER&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;CENTER_CROP&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code&gt;CENTER&lt;/code&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FIT_XY:&lt;/strong&gt; Considers the X and Y scale so the original image matches to the predicted dimensions for the UI visualization. It can change the image proportion.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FIT_CENTER:&lt;/strong&gt; Considers a computed scale that will keep the image&amp;rsquo;s original proportion and also guarantees that it entirely fits on the UI&amp;rsquo;s space. At least two axes (X or Y) will serve. The result is centralized on the image&amp;rsquo;s local.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CENTER_CROP:&lt;/strong&gt; Considers an uniform scale (keeping the image&amp;rsquo;s proportion) so both image&amp;rsquo;s dimensions (width and height) will be equal or bigger than the dimension correspondent to UI&amp;rsquo;s view.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CENTER:&lt;/strong&gt; center image that will be visualized, but not redimensioned.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;

      </description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Docs: Imagepath</title>
      <link>https://zupit.github.io/docs-beagle/docs/api/components/ui/image/imagepath/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://zupit.github.io/docs-beagle/docs/api/components/ui/image/imagepath/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;what-is-it&#34;&gt;What is it?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ImagePath allows you to define how the image will be loaded, which &lt;strong&gt;can be locally or remotely.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;how-to-use-it&#34;&gt;How to use it?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;imagepathlocal&#34;&gt;ImagePath.Local&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It will reference a image that is on locais.JSONKotlin DSL assets. Your structure is represented by the attributes below:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
&lt;thead&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;th style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Attribute&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Type&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Definition&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/thead&gt;
&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;webUrl&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;String&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;Absolute or relative image path to be downloaded.&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;mobileId&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;String&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;Image&amp;rsquo;s identifier that was previously registered on mobile platforms.&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It will refer an image that it is already in the local assets.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&#34;nav nav-tabs&#34; id=&#34;t128&#34; role=&#34;tablist&#34;&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;nav-item&#34;&gt;&lt;a data-toggle=&#34;tab&#34; class=&#34;nav-link active&#34; href=&#34;#t128-0&#34; role=&#34;tab&#34; aria-controls=&#34;t128-0&#34; aria-selected=&#34;true&#34;&gt;JSON&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	  
		&lt;li class=&#34;nav-item&#34;&gt;&lt;a data-toggle=&#34;tab&#34; class=&#34;nav-link&#34; href=&#34;#t128-1&#34; role=&#34;tab&#34; aria-controls=&#34;t128-1&#34;&gt;Kotlin DSL&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;tab-content&#34; id=&#34;t128&#34;&gt;&lt;div id=&#34;t128-0&#34; class=&#34;tab-pane show active&#34; role=&#34;tabpanel&#34; aria-labelledby=&#34;t128-0&#34;&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre style=&#34;background-color:#f8f8f8;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-javascript&#34; data-lang=&#34;javascript&#34;&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#4e9a06&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;_beagleImagePath_&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#4e9a06&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;local&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#000;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#4e9a06&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;url&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#4e9a06&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;/imagemlocal.png&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#000;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#4e9a06&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;mobileId&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#4e9a06&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;imagemlocal&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span style=&#34;color:#000;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div id=&#34;t128-1&#34; class=&#34;tab-pane&#34; role=&#34;tabpanel&#34; aria-labelledby=&#34;t128-1&#34;&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;ImagePath.Local(
  webUrl = &amp;quot;/imagePath.png&amp;quot;,
  mobileId = &amp;quot;imagePath&amp;quot;
)
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;imagepathremote&#34;&gt;ImagePath.Remote&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It will reference an image that its hosted on another host or it&amp;rsquo;s related to its own server.JSONKotlin DSL. Your structure is represented by the attributes below:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
&lt;thead&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;th style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Attribute&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Type&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;Required&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Definition&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/thead&gt;
&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;remoteUrl&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;String&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;✓&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;Absolute or relative image path to be downloaded.&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;placeholder&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;​&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://docs.usebeagle.io/api/componentes/ui/image/imagepath-1#imagepath-local&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ImagePath.Local&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;​&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;It&amp;rsquo;s possible to pass a local asset on the app that will be shown meanwhile the remote URL is loaded.&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It will refer to an image that is hosted in another host or a relative one in the own server.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&#34;nav nav-tabs&#34; id=&#34;t128&#34; role=&#34;tablist&#34;&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;nav-item&#34;&gt;&lt;a data-toggle=&#34;tab&#34; class=&#34;nav-link active&#34; href=&#34;#t128-0&#34; role=&#34;tab&#34; aria-controls=&#34;t128-0&#34; aria-selected=&#34;true&#34;&gt;JSON&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	  
		&lt;li class=&#34;nav-item&#34;&gt;&lt;a data-toggle=&#34;tab&#34; class=&#34;nav-link&#34; href=&#34;#t128-1&#34; role=&#34;tab&#34; aria-controls=&#34;t128-1&#34;&gt;Kotlin DSL&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;tab-content&#34; id=&#34;t128&#34;&gt;&lt;div id=&#34;t128-0&#34; class=&#34;tab-pane show active&#34; role=&#34;tabpanel&#34; aria-labelledby=&#34;t128-0&#34;&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre style=&#34;background-color:#f8f8f8;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-javascript&#34; data-lang=&#34;javascript&#34;&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#4e9a06&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;_beagleImagePath_&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#4e9a06&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;remote&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#000;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#4e9a06&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;url&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#4e9a06&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;https://i.ibb.co/k9tYwtX/selo-do-exemplo-28420393.jpg&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#000;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#4e9a06&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;placeholder&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#000;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#4e9a06&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;_beagleImagePath_&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#4e9a06&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;local&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#000;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#4e9a06&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;url&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#4e9a06&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;/imagemlocal.png&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#000;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#4e9a06&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;mobileId&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#4e9a06&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;imagemlocal&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#000;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span style=&#34;color:#000;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div id=&#34;t128-1&#34; class=&#34;tab-pane&#34; role=&#34;tabpanel&#34; aria-labelledby=&#34;t128-1&#34;&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;ImagePath.Remote(
  remoteUrl = &amp;quot;https://i.ibb.co/k9tYwtX/selo-do-exemplo-28420393.jpg&amp;quot;,
  placeHolder = ImagePath.Local(
      webUrl = &amp;quot;/imagePath.png&amp;quot;,
      mobileId = &amp;quot;imagePath&amp;quot;
  )
)
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

      </description>
